videos.headline: Holy Cross' back-to-back buckets punches their ticket to Patriot League Championship
videos.description: Cara McCormack splashes a triple from the top of the key then Lindsay Berger's second-effort dagger secures the win for the Crusaders.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Holy Cross' back-to-back buckets punches their ticket to Patriot League Championship) 2024/03/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kaitlyn Flanagan takes it coast-to-coast for a Holy Cross basket
videos.description: Kaitlyn Flanagan takes the rock coast-to-coast and lays it in to pad the Crusaders' lead.
